<script setup lang="ts">
import { useAnimate } from 'motion-v';
import type { AnimatedIconProps, AnimatedIconHandle } from '../types/types';

const props = withDefaults(defineProps<AnimatedIconProps>(), {
  size: 24,
  color: 'currentColor',
  strokeWidth: 2,
  className: '',
});

const [scope, animate] = useAnimate();

const start = () => {
  animate(
    '.dolphin',
    { y: [0, -2, 0] },
    { duration: 0.8, ease: 'easeInOut' }
  );
  animate(
    '.eye',
    { scale: [1, 1.5, 1] },
    { duration: 0.3, ease: 'easeInOut' }
  );
};

const stop = () => {
  animate(
    '.dolphin, .eye',
    { y: 0, scale: 1 },
    { duration: 0.2, ease: 'easeInOut' }
  );
};

defineExpose({
  startAnimation: start,
  stopAnimation: stop,
} satisfies AnimatedIconHandle);
</script>

<template>
  <svg
    ref="scope"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    :width="size"
    :height="size"
    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
    fill="none"
    :stroke="color"
    :stroke-width="strokeWidth"
    stroke-linecap="round"
    stroke-linejoin="round"
    :class="['cursor-pointer', className]"
    @mouseenter="start"
    @mouseleave="stop"
  >
    <path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none" />
    <path
      class="dolphin"
      d="M13 21c-1.427 -1.026 -3.59 -3.854 -4 -6c-.486 .77 -1.501 2 -2 2c-1.499 -.888 -.574 -3.973 0 -6c-1.596 -1.433 -2.468 -2.458 -2.5 -4c-3.35 -3.44 -.444 -5.27 2.5 -3h1c8.482 .5 6.421 8.07 9 11.5c2.295 .522 3.665 2.254 5 3.5c-2.086 -.2 -2.784 -.344 -3.5 0c.478 1.64 2.123 2.2 3.5 3"
    />
    <path
      class="eye"
      :style="{ transformOrigin: '9 7' }"
      d="M9 7h.01"
    />
  </svg>
</template>
